6 SECTION 2. There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Reserve for Retiree
7 Cost-of-Living Adjustments the sum of two hundred fifty million dollars ($250,000,000) in
8 recurring funds for the 2025-2026 fiscal year to implement Section 1 of this act.
9 SECTION 3. This act becomes effective July 1, 2025.
